Subject: CLINTON: War Powers Resolution on Bosnia 4.14.93
Date: 15 Apr 1993 09:27:05 -0400
Organization: Project GNU, Free Software Foundation,
    675 Mass. Ave., Cambridge, MA  02139, USA +1 (617) 876-3296
Lines: 102
Sender: daemon@ai.mit.edu
Message-ID: <1qjnr9INN7d@life.ai.mit.edu>
