References: <1993Apr12.191522.22362@scic.intel.com> <EMERY.93Apr12171135@goldfinger.mitre.org> <C5G8AB.243@ecf.toronto.edu> <1993Apr14.121823.21851@oneb.almanac.bc.ca>
