References: <1993Apr15.013651.11353@tijc02.uucp> <1993Apr15.170731.8797@isc-br.isc-br.com> <16APR199317110543@rigel.tamu.edu> <1993Apr18.172531.10946@isc-br.isc-br.com>
Date: Sun, 18 Apr 1993 20:22:16 GMT
