Subject: CLINTON: Remarks to Law Enforcement Leaders
Date: 15 Apr 1993 22:02:07 -0400
Organization: Project GNU, Free Software Foundation,
    675 Mass. Ave., Cambridge, MA  02139, USA +1 (617) 876-3296
